  },
  {
    title: "Security & Compliance Planning",
    description: "Legal technology requires the highest security standards. We design a security architecture that protects attorney-client privilege, ensures data confidentiality, and meets all regulatory compliance requirements for your jurisdiction."
  },
  {
    title: "Custom Development & Integration",
    description: "Our development team builds your legal technology solution using secure, enterprise-grade technologies. We integrate with your existing tools (calendar systems, accounting software, document storage) and provide regular demos throughout development."
  },
  {
    title: "Training & Seamless Deployment",
    description: "We provide comprehensive training for attorneys, paralegals, and support staff. Our deployment process is carefully planned to ensure minimal disruption to your practice, with data migration support and go-live assistance."
  },
  {
    title: "Ongoing Support & Maintenance",
    description: "Your practice evolves, and so should your technology. We provide ongoing support, security updates, and feature enhancements. Our team is always available to help you maximize the value of your legal technology investment."
